LatexCommand citep
key "Solow:1956tg"

\end_inset

 since it converges toward a steady states where all variables grow at a
 constant rate.
 Disaggregated in 37 sectors with an explicit distinction between 13 types
 of energy sources and five types of transports, it allows for the neo-Keynesian
 short/medium term macroeconomic modeling approach to catch-up with the
 most advanced CGEM in terms of sectoral analysis.
 In addition, its hybrid structure regarding the specification of the behavior
 of households overcomes the restrictions imposed by nested utility approach
 assumed in standard CGEM.
\end_layout

